To create a package:
1 - Make sure the Package tab is selected.
2 - Click the word 'Packages' on the Package tab.
3 - In the dialog that appears, type the name of the package.
4 - In the Add Documents dialog, select the documents you want to include in the package.

You can also create a package by dragging one or more files from Windows Explorer(TM) onto the white part of the package tab.